# 🚀 Crypto Market Dashboard

A simple JavaScript app that displays live cryptocurrency data using the CoinGecko API.

---

## 📸 Preview

> Add a screenshot of your app here  
> (e.g. `![App Screenshot](./screenshot.png)`)

---

## ✨ Features

- 📊 View top cryptocurrencies by market cap
- 💱 Toggle between USD and EUR
- 🔍 Search coins by name or symbol (no API re-fetch)
- 🔄 Auto-refresh every 60 seconds
- 💾 Saves selected currency using localStorage
- 📈 Shows 1h, 24h, and 7d price changes
- 🎨 Colour-coded price changes (green/red)
- ⏳ Loading & error states
